INSERT INTO `wwd_posts` VALUES (723,1,'2013-09-14 10:16:45','2013-09-14 15:16:45','[bgsection pex_attr_title=\"RAY LI\" pex_attr_subtitle=\"founder &amp; CEO\" pex_attr_undefined=\"undefined\" pex_attr_style=\"section-dark\" pex_attr_bgcolor=\"454849\" pex_attr_image=\"\" pex_attr_imageopacity=\"0.4\" pex_attr_titlecolor=\"ffffff\" pex_attr_textcolor=\"ffffff\" pex_attr_bgimagestyle=\"parallax-scroll\"][/bgsection]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSuitable founder Ray Li didnât intend to start a company.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGrowing up, Ray always enjoyed helping his mates dress better.Â  Whether it was a trip to the local mall in college or to various fashion districts after moving to New York City, it was fun to help his buddies look good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBut it was never just about the external appearances.Â  The reward was also in helping them believe more in themselves through the process.Â  The common refrain was, âno, I could never pull that off.âÂ  So it was just as much about finding the right perspective as it was about finding the right piece.Â  It was about unlocking the gentleman in the everyday man.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSo Suitable was conceived before it ever started. Because the suit is the cornerstone of style.Â  An amazing suit highlights the man.Â  A bad suit is worse than no suit at all.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nRay started his career in management consulting with Deloitte Consulting.Â  Wanting to do something with both head and heart, he switched over to be a brand strategist with Interbrand, a brand consultancy.Â Â  As Ray learned more about suit design &amp; production on the side, Suitable began to form.Â  Ray realized he could combine his personal passion with his professional background in brand building to deliver a best-in-class experience at a game changing price point.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nToday, Ray lives in New York City with his wife, drinks too much coffee, takes his bourbon neat and is thrilled to be part of the Suitable team.','Meet our founder','','publish','open','open','','founder','','','2013-09-25 20:05:24','2013-09-26 01:05:24','',0,'http://www.suitablenyc.com/?page_id=723',0,'page','',0);
